Product Description: We specialize in designing and supplying premium-quality Stadium Tensile Structures that combine strength, durability, and modern aesthetics. Engineered with advanced tensile membrane technology, these structures are ideal for large-span coverage, providing shade, comfort, and a striking architectural appeal.
Key Features: High-strength PVC / PTFE / HDPE fabric Lightweight yet robust steel framework UV, rain, and wind resistant Modern &amp; innovative design options Low maintenance with long service life Custom sizes, shapes &amp; colors available Applications: Sports Stadiums Athletic Grounds Cricket &amp; Football Arenas Event &amp; Exhibition Areas Public Gathering Spaces Specifications: Fabric: PVC Coated / PTFE / HDPE Membrane Structure: Mild Steel / Galvanized Steel Span: Large clear-span coverage (customizable) Finish: Powder coated / Painted frame Lifespan: 15–30 years depending on
